      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/16/3",
      "text": [
        ": قال أبو عبد الله: يا محمد! من أخبرك عنا توقيتاً فلا تهابن أن تُكذبه، فإنا لا نوقّت لأحد وقتاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(3) Ali bin Ahmad narrated from Obaydillah bin Musa al-Alawi from Ya’qoob bin Yazeed from Muhammad bin Abu Omayr from Abdullah bin Bukayr from Muhammad bin Muslim that Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) had said: “O Muhammad, whoever narrates to you a tradition from us talking about timing, do not hesitate to consider him as a liar because we do not time to anyone.”"
        ]
      }
    },
